<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>32</hymn_number>
<author>Thangngur</author>
<title>Kristmas !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nunnawpna Krismas na pak ka tan lai un,
 Kumpi muolliem ding hi zuih guo a;
 Chawnban huntu mahleng nungtieng nei sawn hi,
 Ka hun phal puou ie.

[V2]
 Muolliem loin cham in.
 Ka hun ngai ui cham in;
 Seino guol in gibang ka hunkhen phal puou;
 Nunnawpna Kristmas

[V3]
 2. Kumpi muolliem ding hi zuilo thei kei puoi;
 Chieh loa nichuong thei ding kei puoi;
 Na nawpna pakuh tun muolliem ding kei tai,
 Dam takin chibai

[V4]
 Ka hung kivel kit tieng,
 Dawn bang kituok hitiu;
 Vangsakna thak tawh kilawp kit ngei hitiu
 Dam takin chibai.

[V5]
 3. Nuoi simlei um tunga Lalpa guot bangin
 Gibang kikhen lo thei I hi puou;
 Na la gihawih lunggil ah daibang a cham,
 Nunnawpna Kristmas.

[V6]
 Pathien in ei veng hen,
 Dawn bang kituok kit di'n;
 Na thutiem vangsakna kha puon hung kitin
 Dam takin Krismas.</lyrics>
</song>